#

Hearty Beef and Barley Soup

75 min
$12.5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 6

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow FatNutritious

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodEasy Meal

Description

A comforting and nutritious soup packed with tender beef, wholesome barley, and vegetables, perfect for a cozy meal.

Ingredients

  • beef chuck: 1 lb
  • barley: 1/2 cup
  • carrots: 2, diced
  • celery: 2 stalks, diced
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • beef broth: 6 cups
  • bay leaves: 2
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • thyme: 1 tsp
